Hdp is a new hdf utility currently under development. 

This directory contains the draft design (commandline.draft1) and source code for hdp. 
File report.Apr reports the current status of hdp and presents some samples of its usage. 
There is also a Makefile.in for ../configure to produce the Makefile.

Please send your bug reports, comments and suggestions to hdfhelp@ncsa.uiuc.edu.



